First Lady Melania Trump spoke with Mrs. Akie Abe of Japan and expressed gratitude for the efforts of Mrs. Abe and her husband, Prime Minister Shinzo Abe, in strengthening the alliance between the United States and Japan. Melania Trump also congratulated Mrs. Abe on her family's success, highlighting that Prime Minister Abe is the longest continuously serving Prime Minister in Japan's history. The First Lady wished Prime Minister Abe a speedy recovery and good health. Melania Trump and Mrs. Abe expressed their anticipation for maintaining their close friendship in the future.